description: Wake up to calming ocean views & enjoy your morning coffee on a private deck overlooking Dorchester Bay—or head up to the roof deck for panoramic views of downtown Boston. With just under 1,000 sf, this thoughtfully designed condo delivers exceptional features: a spa-like primary bath w/ radiant heated floors & a backlit niche, in-wall Polk Audio speakers, & a smart lighting system that elevates everyday living. Newly refinished hardwood floors & gas fireplace add comfort & style, while two spacious primary closets offer excellent storage. A versatile bonus room provides the perfect space for a home office, nursery, or gym. Situated directly across from a the Dorchester Heights Monument & just moments from the beach, you’ll have no shortage of outdoor escapes. Ideally located between East and West Broadway, enjoy easy access to Southie’s best dining, nightlife, & neighborhood staples. 53 Thomas Park is the epitome of urban living—peaceful at home, yet steps from the action.
